songs.title: Medieval Cathedral
songs.author: audial-preset
songs.snippet:
setcpm(50)

// organ drone
$: note("<[d2,a2,d3] [c2,g2,c3] [bb1,f2,bb2] [c2,g2,c3]>")
  .s("sawtooth")
  .lpf(400)
  .gain(0.25)
  .slow(4)
  .room(0.8)

// high overtones
$: note("d5 ~ ~ a5 ~ ~ f5 ~ ~ g5 ~ ~")
  .s("sine")
  .gain(0.1)
  .delay(0.5)
  .room(0.9)
  .slow(3)

// bell
$: note("d6 ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~")
  .s("sine")
  .gain(0.08)
  .room(0.95)
  .delay(0.7)
  .slow(4)

// sub bass
$: note("d2 ~ ~ ~ c2 ~ ~ ~ bb1 ~ ~ ~ c2 ~ ~ ~")
  .s("sine")
  .lpf(120)
  .gain(0.3)
  .slow(4)
